OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,FA woman from Lancashire has told how
OL,7,Fshe's helping a tech firm create
OL,8,Fartificial intelligence which can
OL,9,Fsupport people living with Dementia.
OL,11,FThe first Alzheimer's Avatar, named
OL,12,FLiv, is being described as a potential
OL,13,Ftechnological breakthrough.
OL,15,FDesigned using the experiences of
OL,16,Fthose who have the disease, it helps
OL,17,Fprovide social interaction and
OL,18,Fmaintain communication skills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
