OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,FMore than 100,000 people in the North
OL,7,FWest live with some form of the
OL,8,Fcondition - with that number expected
OL,9,Fto rise to nearly 150,000 by 2040.
OL,11,FGail Gregory, a 56-year-old from
OL,12,FBlackpool was diagnosed with young-
OL,13,Fonset Alzheimer's disease.
OL,15,FShe participated in the focus groups
OL,16,Fwhich informed the development of the
OL,17,Ftech and knows first hand the
OL,18,Fimportance of realistic and relatable
OL,19,Fadvice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
