OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,FGail said: "The thing is, when you get
OL,7,Fa diagnosis of dementia, like I did
OL,8,Ffive years ago, when when you leave
OL,9,Fthat clinic or consultation room, you
OL,10,Ffeel quite numb and everything's sort
OL,11,Fof a blur.
OL,13,F"So you come out of that room and you
OL,14,Fhaven't answered the questions that
OL,15,Fyou you might want to answer, because
OL,16,Fit's just been a big shock for you."
OL,18,FGail got help through an online
OL,19,Fsupport group recording video diaries
OL,20,Fabout her life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
