OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,FThat support and expertise has now
OL,7,Fbeen turned into an AI avatar, with
OL,8,Fthe hope even more people can be
OL,9,Fhelped.
OL,11,FSteve Milton, Director, Innovations in
OL,12,FDementia and project lead for the
OL,13,FDementia Diaries, explained: "Lenovo
OL,14,Fcame to us and said, 'How would you
OL,15,Flike us to help you take all of this
OL,16,Fwisdom and all of this knowledge and
OL,17,Fall of this compassion and put it into
OL,18,Fa virtual avatar that has been named
OL,19,FLiv?'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
