OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1729244897
OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,F"That can be there as a direct contact
OL,7,Fbetween all the wisdom in these
OL,8,Fdiaries, and people who are sitting at
OL,9,Fhome having just received their
OL,10,Fdiagnosis of dementia - and we thought
OL,11,Fthat was a pretty good idea."
OL,13,FThe scientists brought the technology
OL,14,Fto Gail's house so she could try it
OL,15,Fout. She said: "It was quite scary at
OL,16,Ffirst, because you're speaking to a
OL,17,Frobot, but once you get used to that,
OL,18,Fit's quite useful.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
