OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1729244897
OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,F"The strangest thing was, though,
OL,7,Fbecause I'm from Lancashire and I have
OL,8,Fa very broad Lancashire accent, she
OL,9,Fwas actually picking up some of my
OL,10,FLancashire accent, which was quite
OL,11,Fscary at first.
OL,13,F"But it brought a few laughs in the
OL,14,Froom."
OL,16,FGail added: "I'd like people to know
OL,17,Fthat dementia is not all about the end
OL,18,Fstages. I would urge people to find
OL,19,Fpeer support groups and get involved,
OL,20,Fand your life will change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
