OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1729244897
OL,3,CFirst-of-its-kind AI Avatar provides
OL,4,Csupport for people living with dementia
OL,6,F"I've turned everything around now,
OL,7,Ffrom being negative and not knowing
OL,8,Fwhat was going to happen to my life,
OL,9,Fto being positive."
OL,11,FThe AI avatar isn't publicly available
OL,12,Fyet as the scheme needs more funding,
OL,13,Fbut it's hoped this technology could
OL,14,Fone day help make a positive
OL,15,Fdifference to the millions of people
OL,16,Fliving with Alzheimer's and dementia.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
